{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-86-cuboid-route","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 86: Putanja pravougaonika sa tri strane","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pauk S nalazi se u jednom uglu pravougaonog kvadra dimenzija 6 × 5 × 3, a muva F u suprotnom uglu. Krećući se samo po površini kvadra, najkraći put u pravoj liniji od S do F iznosi 10 i prikazan je na slici.</p>\n<img alt=\"dijagram puta pauka i muve od jednog ugla pravougaonog kvadra do suprotnog ugla\" src=\"https://cdn-media-1.freecodecamp.org/project-euler/cuboid-route.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Međutim, postoji do tri kandidata za „najkraći put“ za bilo koji trokut, a najkraći put ne uvek ima dužinu celog broja.</p>\n<p>Može se pokazati da postoji tačno <code>2060</code> različitih pravougaonih kvadara, ne računajući rotacije, sa celobrojnim dimenzijama do maksimalne veličine M × M × M, kod kojih najkraći put ima celobrojnu dužinu kada je M = 100. Ovo je najmanja vrednost M za koju broj rešenja prvi put prelazi dve hiljade; za M = 99 broj rešenja je <code>1975</code>.</p>\n<p>Pronađi najmanju vrednost M ili broj rešenja koji prvi premaši <code>n</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3c31000cf542c50fed5","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302200,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-86-cuboid-route"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function cuboidRoute(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncuboidRoute(2000);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>cuboidRoute(2000)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof cuboidRoute(2000) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>cuboidRoute(2000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>100</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(cuboidRoute(2000), 100);"},{"text":"<p><code>cuboidRoute(25000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>320</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(cuboidRoute(25000), 320);"},{"text":"<p><code>cuboidRoute(500000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1309</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(cuboidRoute(500000), 1309);"},{"text":"<p><code>cuboidRoute(1000000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>1818</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(cuboidRoute(1000000), 1818);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-86-cuboid-route","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-87-prime-power-triples","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-85-counting-rectangles","id":"5900f3c31000cf542c50fed5","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-86-cuboid-route"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}